1
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:34,320
=Hold a Court Now=

2
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:38,140
=Episode 25=

3
00:01:40,750 --> 00:01:42,029
The plaintiff claims the defendant

4
00:01:42,030 --> 00:01:45,159
should return the child support
for Wang Yuanbao from birth until now,

5
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:47,359
covering twenty-eight years,

6
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:49,879
totaling 1,387,000 yuan.

7
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:51,359
No, forget it.

8
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:52,600
Sir,

9
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:54,359
do you confirm
that you are giving up this claim?

10
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:55,469
Yes.

11
00:01:55,470 --> 00:01:56,589
Reason?

12
00:01:56,590 --> 00:01:58,510
If I am giving it up,
what reason is there?

13
00:01:58,880 --> 00:01:59,829
I need to confirm with you

14
00:01:59,830 --> 00:02:02,669
whether you fully understand
the consequences of this decision,

15
00:02:02,670 --> 00:02:04,240
to avoid any future disputes.

16
00:02:04,390 --> 00:02:05,669
Judge Shen, do not worry.

17
00:02:05,670 --> 00:02:07,910
I know exactly what I am doing.

18
00:02:08,310 --> 00:02:09,119
Confirmed,

19
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,390
I'm giving up the claim.

20
00:02:13,910 --> 00:02:15,239
What is the reason?

21
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,350
I owe her.

22
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:22,480
Could you be more specific?

23
00:02:23,350 --> 00:02:24,670
Back then,

24
00:02:25,470 --> 00:02:27,320
she was quite good-looking,

25
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:29,000
and had many suitors.

26
00:02:29,440 --> 00:02:31,560
Among them was the village chief's son.

27
00:02:32,470 --> 00:02:34,160
She chose me at the time.

28
00:02:36,470 --> 00:02:39,280
If she had chosen
the village chief's son,

29
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,760
she would have been living
in a three-story house long ago.

30
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,959
Anyway, she cannot pay me back,

31
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:47,880
so I will just treat this money
as compensation for her.

32
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:51,480
Please wait a moment.

33
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:52,959
What is going on?

34
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,320
The computer lost power.

35
00:02:55,190 --> 00:02:56,390
Restart it quickly.

36
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:02,110
Why are you not using a laptop?

37
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:04,350
The laptop is broken.
It is being repaired.

38
00:03:07,310 --> 00:03:08,789
Sorry, Judge Shen.

39
00:03:08,790 --> 00:03:10,629
Part of the document was lost.

40
00:03:10,630 --> 00:03:11,999
How much was lost?

41
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:12,999
About from

42
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,189
when madam
and the village chief's son were dating.

43
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:16,189
I... I did not.

44
00:03:16,190 --> 00:03:17,309
No, I...

45
00:03:17,310 --> 00:03:19,959
I did not say she was dating
the village chief's son.

46
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:22,350
I said the village chief's son
was pursuing her,

47
00:03:23,070 --> 00:03:24,600
and she chose me.

48
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:30,160
Sir,

49
00:03:30,310 --> 00:03:31,630
sorry about this,

50
00:03:31,750 --> 00:03:34,230
you will have to say it again.

51
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,559
From where?

52
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,600
From

53
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:37,839
Madam Qiu,

54
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,720
when she was young, was very pretty.

55
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:42,110
Well, when she

56
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,559
was young,

57
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,230
was the beauty of the village,

58
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:47,760
a well-known beauty.

59
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:49,360
Young men
from all the surrounding villages,

60
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,760
none of them
did not have their eyes on her.

61
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:55,880
Yes, I mean she looked decent,

62
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:58,230
and had many suitors.

63
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,510
She chose me.

64
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,440
Dad.

65
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:25,150
Dad.

66
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,240
Dad.

67
00:04:29,390 --> 00:04:30,590
Dad.

68
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:36,270
Dad.

69
00:04:39,150 --> 00:04:40,880
B... Ba.

70
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:46,829
Ba.

71
00:04:46,830 --> 00:04:47,880
Dad.

72
00:04:48,630 --> 00:04:50,000
Ba.

73
00:04:51,150 --> 00:04:52,510
Ba.

74
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:54,389
(Conference Room In Use)

75
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:55,389
Ms. Shu,

76
00:04:55,390 --> 00:04:57,710
Shi Xiaomei has really found a job.

77
00:04:57,800 --> 00:05:00,239
She has even planned out

78
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,629
the children's future lives.

79
00:05:01,630 --> 00:05:03,710
Given the current conditions,

80
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:06,200
is it possible to support awarding

81
00:05:06,270 --> 00:05:07,630
all three children to her?

82
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:10,239
I think that would be difficult.

83
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,829
Shi Xiaomei said

84
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:14,510
that her job is in content creation.

85
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:16,069
Although she does not need to clock in,

86
00:05:16,070 --> 00:05:17,479
and the income is not low,

87
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:19,030
it is unstable.

88
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:21,039
Maintaining their current
standard of living

89
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,599
would be unlikely.

90
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,359
So she still needs

91
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,919
child support from the man.

92
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:27,440
Then Duan Ziping will definitely
have to pay child support.

93
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:30,879
Child support
is a mandatory legal obligation.

94
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:33,920
The parent who does not
have direct custody must pay child support.

95
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:36,949
However, there may
be uncertainties in enforcement.

96
00:05:36,950 --> 00:05:38,559
Duan Ziping's income

97
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,919
mainly depends on his mother.

98
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,239
He does not have much money.

99
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,799
If all three children

100
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:44,479
are awarded to Shi Xiaomei,

101
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:46,949
and the man refuses
to pay child support,

102
00:05:46,950 --> 00:05:48,599
we cannot gamble with

103
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:50,510
the children's future.

104
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:52,390
That would be too irresponsible.

105
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:57,149
Then what if we use

106
00:05:57,150 --> 00:05:58,999
a joint custody arrangement?

107
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,119
We could have

108
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:02,679
the grandmother and the mother
take turns raising the children,

109
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:04,919
on a cycle of one to two months.

110
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,440
The children have
not yet started school,

111
00:06:06,440 --> 00:06:08,120
so changes in environment
would have less impact.

112
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:10,630
As I recall,
some of our counterpart courts

113
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,590
have made rulings like this.

114
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:16,479
But the main conflict in this case

115
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,799
is not Duan Ziping,

116
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:19,439
but the children's grandmother.

117
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:20,309
The grandmother insists

118
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:22,879
on raising two of the children herself,

119
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:25,560
and wants all the children
to stay by her side.

120
00:06:25,750 --> 00:06:28,120
So that will be difficult to resolve.

121
00:06:29,310 --> 00:06:31,070
Then after all this discussion,

122
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:32,999
it seems the only option

123
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:35,269
is to award the twins to the father.

124
00:06:35,270 --> 00:06:36,709
At present, that seems to be the case.

125
00:06:36,710 --> 00:06:37,949
And I think

126
00:06:37,950 --> 00:06:40,679
we should have both sides reach
a settlement as soon as possible.

127
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:41,999
Every hearing

128
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:44,200
is not only tormenting the three adults,

129
00:06:44,270 --> 00:06:46,440
but also very painful for the children.

130
00:06:47,750 --> 00:06:48,949
Then we must ensure

131
00:06:48,950 --> 00:06:51,120
Shi Xiaomei's visitation rights.

132
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,679
I hope she can understand.

133
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:55,240
What she said is not correct.

134
00:06:55,390 --> 00:06:57,590
My mother disliked her because she

135
00:06:57,630 --> 00:06:59,200
does not talk much,

136
00:07:00,390 --> 00:07:02,630
does not greet people, and cries easily.

137
00:07:03,270 --> 00:07:05,680
Back then, I was working at the mine,

138
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:07,559
and she was at home making steamed buns.

139
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:09,189
Just because they did not look good,

140
00:07:09,190 --> 00:07:10,880
my mother said a few harsh words to her.

141
00:07:10,950 --> 00:07:12,830
Then, in the middle of heavy snow,

142
00:07:12,950 --> 00:07:14,749
she ran over twenty miles by herself

143
00:07:14,750 --> 00:07:17,000
to the mine to complain to me.

144
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,270
By the time she arrived,

145
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:21,680
she was almost frozen stiff.

146
00:07:23,310 --> 00:07:24,509
When she saw me,

147
00:07:24,510 --> 00:07:26,240
she threw herself
into my arms and cried.

148
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:28,119
After she finished crying,

149
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:30,560
she took out
a big steamed bun from her coat

150
00:07:30,950 --> 00:07:32,239
and asked me to judge.

151
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,470
This...

152
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:35,039
This bun

153
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:37,000
was as big as a piglet.

154
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,470
So I said,

155
00:07:40,830 --> 00:07:42,680
my mother was not wrong about you.

156
00:07:43,310 --> 00:07:45,320
And she cried even harder.

157
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:49,240
Yes, the buns did not look very good,

158
00:07:50,510 --> 00:07:52,360
but they tasted great.

159
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:57,030
Thin skin, generous filling,
sweet and fragrant.

160
00:07:57,510 --> 00:07:59,680
She had been keeping it inside her coat,

161
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:01,830
and when I ate it,

162
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:04,150
it was still warm.

163
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,120
I am very sorry.

164
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:19,439
What is it this time?

165
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:20,760
The power is out again.

166
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:25,320
This computer really needs fixing.

167
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,630
Okay.

168
00:08:30,950 --> 00:08:32,079
Sir,

169
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,669
I am very sorry,

170
00:08:33,670 --> 00:08:34,879
but I may have to trouble you

171
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:36,350
to say it again.

172
00:08:36,670 --> 00:08:38,040
From where this time?

173
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,830
From

174
00:08:40,750 --> 00:08:42,680
the part where Madam Qiu

175
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:45,200
ran over twenty miles
in the snow to find you.

176
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:47,040
Right.

177
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:49,429
She was at home making steamed buns,

178
00:08:49,430 --> 00:08:51,320
arguing with my mother.

179
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,509
She went out alone,

180
00:08:53,510 --> 00:08:54,549
in the heavy snow,

181
00:08:54,550 --> 00:08:56,479
and ran more than twenty miles at night

182
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:57,950
to the mine to find me.

183
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:37,359
(Qingcheng District People's Court)
In order to further improve

184
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:39,840
(Joint Anti-Domestic Violence Working Conference)
public awareness of anti-domestic violence,

185
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:42,789
and to enhance a multi-department
coordinated mechanism,

186
00:09:42,790 --> 00:09:44,920
Qingcheng District People's Court
has joined hands with

187
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:47,200
the District Working Committee,
the Political and Legal Affairs Commission,

188
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,880
the Publicity Department,
the Health Commission,

189
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:52,749
the District Women's Federation,
Tianhai Chenxi Legal Aid Work Center,

190
00:09:52,750 --> 00:09:55,789
Qingcheng Student Community
Service Center,

191
00:09:55,790 --> 00:09:58,199
and other regional women's organizations

192
00:09:58,200 --> 00:10:00,110
and related member units

193
00:10:00,450 --> 00:10:03,039
to convene at our Qingcheng District
People's Court

194
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:06,750
a seminar on a one-stop coordinated
anti-domestic violence mechanism.

195
00:10:12,550 --> 00:10:14,780
(Mediation Room 1 In Use)
You do not want to help me anymore, do you?

196
00:10:17,800 --> 00:10:19,520
I have found a job.

197
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:21,319
This is all true.

198
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,719
I am not lying to you.

199
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:24,400
I have proof of employment.

200
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:27,920
I... I am not lying. This is all true.

201
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:30,000
We are not trying
to help one side over the other.

202
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,679
You and your husband

203
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:34,039
can no longer continue your marriage.

204
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:35,919
At this stage,
the most important thing for you

205
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:36,839
is how to ensure

206
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,880
your children's future quality of life.

207
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:40,479
And we truly hope

208
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:42,999
that you can reach
an out-of-court settlement.

209
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,320
Because in that way,

210
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:46,039
in the future we can still

211
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:47,279
revisit and discuss things,

212
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:48,920
and there will be room
for further negotiation.

213
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,600
No.

214
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:52,999
I will not accept being separated
from my children.

215
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:55,720
None of us want to separate you
from your children.

216
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,239
But right now,

217
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,519
you need to put yourself in their shoes

218
00:10:58,520 --> 00:11:00,119
and consider their future

219
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,400
quality of life.

220
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:04,080
If it is just a matter of child support,

221
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:06,119
I can go out and earn money.

222
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,199
Recently,

223
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:09,919
several of my articles have
been accepted by the company.

224
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:12,560
My supervisor
highly recognizes my ability.

225
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:13,519
I am confident

226
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:15,199
that in the future
I can support my children.

227
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,559
I can rely on myself

228
00:11:16,560 --> 00:11:18,320
to raise them.

229
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:20,440
We are all women.

230
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:23,400
Can you not help me?

231
00:11:25,560 --> 00:11:26,960
I am a mother too.

232
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:29,320
I fully understand how you feel.

233
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:32,640
If all three children
are placed with you,

234
00:11:32,880 --> 00:11:35,400
the pressure on your side
will indeed be very heavy.

235
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:36,800
Think about it,

236
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:38,599
Meng needs to attend dance classes,

237
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:40,199
Bei needs to attend football classes.

238
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:42,079
Aside from the cost,

239
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,560
there is also the time commitment.

240
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:46,519
Du is already twelve years old,

241
00:11:46,520 --> 00:11:47,679
and Du

242
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:48,879
has clearly expressed

243
00:11:48,880 --> 00:11:50,799
the wish to live with you.

244
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:52,359
In the days ahead,

245
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:54,720
we can allow Du
to continue living with you.

246
00:11:55,280 --> 00:11:57,280
As for Meng and Bei,

247
00:11:57,800 --> 00:11:59,319
although the two of them

248
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:01,199
will live with their grandmother,

249
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:03,039
we will do our best to ensure

250
00:12:03,040 --> 00:12:05,600
your visitation rights
in their future lives.

251
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:07,519
We will also

252
00:12:07,520 --> 00:12:09,319
fight for your maximum rights
regarding child support.

253
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:11,600
We hope both of you can accept this.

254
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:27,760
Is there really no other way?

255
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:29,999
At the current stage, this may be

256
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:32,240
the best option
for you and the children.

257
00:12:41,760 --> 00:12:44,200
Let us play ball, okay?

258
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:46,360
It is not fun.

259
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,400
Hello.

260
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:56,200
Judge Yu.

261
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:58,080
What is the result?

262
00:13:03,640 --> 00:13:05,039
Regarding the divorce case

263
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:07,599
between the plaintiff Shi Xiaomei
and the defendant Duan Ziping,

264
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:09,239
after in-court mediation,

265
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:10,760
the outcome is as follows.

266
00:13:10,880 --> 00:13:11,639
Given that

267
00:13:11,640 --> 00:13:14,159
the plaintiff's
current income is unstable,

268
00:13:14,160 --> 00:13:15,719
while the defendant

269
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:17,479
has a clearly
stronger financial position

270
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:19,039
and bears no major fault,

271
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:21,579
in accordance with the principle
of the best interests of the minors,

272
00:13:21,580 --> 00:13:23,089
Duan Mengmeng and Duan Beibei

273
00:13:23,090 --> 00:13:24,839
will be raised by their father

274
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:27,360
and live with him.

275
00:13:27,790 --> 00:13:29,439
The eldest daughter, Duan Dudu,

276
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:30,919
will be raised by her mother

277
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:33,760
and live with her.

278
00:13:33,800 --> 00:13:34,999
At the same time, pursuant to

279
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:37,159
Article 1086 of the Civil Code,

280
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:39,119
both parties shall make every effort

281
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:41,439
to accommodate
each other's visitation needs

282
00:13:41,440 --> 00:13:43,480
and must not create obstacles.

283
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:46,039
Do both parties

284
00:13:46,040 --> 00:13:47,439
have any objections?

285
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:48,520
No.

286
00:13:50,760 --> 00:13:52,000
Ms. Shi,

287
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:54,120
do you have any other thoughts?

288
00:13:58,600 --> 00:14:00,679
Please review the contents
of the mediation agreement.

289
00:14:00,680 --> 00:14:02,640
If there are no issues,

290
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:04,560
please sign.

291
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:10,840
Go on, sign it.

292
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:16,240
(Duan Ziping)

293
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:30,879
Xiaomei,

294
00:14:30,880 --> 00:14:32,360
sign it.

295
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:56,960
(Party A Signature: Shi Xiaomei)

296
00:14:58,360 --> 00:15:00,960
(Party A Signature: Shi Xiaomei)

297
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:36,279
Are you not going?

298
00:15:36,280 --> 00:15:39,760
I want to stay with Mom.

299
00:15:46,440 --> 00:15:47,840
Mom.

300
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:53,600
Sweetheart.

301
00:15:54,520 --> 00:15:55,479
It is okay.

302
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:57,680
It is okay. Do not cry.

303
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:05,000
Domestic violence

304
00:16:05,040 --> 00:16:06,479
is not a private family matter.

305
00:16:06,480 --> 00:16:08,079
It is unlawful and a crime.

306
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:09,199
In recent years,

307
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:10,879
cases involving domestic violence

308
00:16:10,880 --> 00:16:12,919
have shown several characteristics.

309
00:16:12,920 --> 00:16:15,560
They are mostly
concentrated in divorce proceedings.

310
00:16:15,640 --> 00:16:18,159
The forms of violence vary,

311
00:16:18,160 --> 00:16:20,040
with physical abuse

312
00:16:20,200 --> 00:16:21,400
being the most common.

313
00:16:21,400 --> 00:16:23,360
(What should be done in cases of domestic violence)
In cases handled by the courts,

314
00:16:23,360 --> 00:16:24,839
the proportion of cases

315
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:28,040
recognized as domestic violence
is relatively low.

316
00:16:29,480 --> 00:16:31,999
In 1999,
the United Nations General Assembly

317
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:33,719
formally adopted a resolution

318
00:16:33,720 --> 00:16:36,119
proposed by the Dominican Republic,

319
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:37,799
with widespread global support

320
00:16:37,800 --> 00:16:39,680
and endorsement

321
00:16:39,800 --> 00:16:42,639
designating November 25 each year

322
00:16:42,640 --> 00:16:45,799
as the International Day for the Elimination
of Violence against Women,

323
00:16:45,800 --> 00:16:47,679
marking the first
international definition

324
00:16:47,680 --> 00:16:50,559
and a global call to eliminate

325
00:16:50,560 --> 00:16:54,000
gender-based violence against women.

326
00:17:01,560 --> 00:17:03,360
That time when the accident
happened at the mine,

327
00:17:04,040 --> 00:17:05,399
I was alone,

328
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:06,960
trapped underground.

329
00:17:07,120 --> 00:17:09,640
No matter how I called out,
there was no answer.

330
00:17:11,360 --> 00:17:13,119
I regretted it then.

331
00:17:13,120 --> 00:17:14,759
I really wanted to slap myself

332
00:17:14,760 --> 00:17:16,280
a few times.

333
00:17:16,360 --> 00:17:17,679
Fengling warned me long ago that

334
00:17:17,680 --> 00:17:19,200
this job was not worth doing.

335
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:22,280
It was risking my life for money.

336
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:25,040
Why did I not listen to her?

337
00:17:25,080 --> 00:17:26,559
Down in the pit, I kept thinking,

338
00:17:26,560 --> 00:17:29,000
if I were given another chance,

339
00:17:30,560 --> 00:17:33,600
I would go find Fengling right away,

340
00:17:35,880 --> 00:17:36,999
eat the big steamed buns she made,

341
00:17:37,000 --> 00:17:39,240
as big as piglets.

342
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,520
I would tell my mother,

343
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:43,560
I would live with Fengling on our own,

344
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:49,680
and no one would be allowed

345
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:51,480
to say a single bad word about my wife.

346
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:06,519
Sorry.

347
00:18:06,520 --> 00:18:08,080
I forgot to turn off the alarm.

348
00:18:09,720 --> 00:18:11,600
It is time to take
his blood clot medication.

349
00:18:11,920 --> 00:18:13,000
All right.

350
00:18:17,640 --> 00:18:18,559
I am not taking it.

351
00:18:18,560 --> 00:18:20,240
You have to.

352
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,719
The doctor said

353
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:23,639
your condition
is very serious right now.

354
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:25,600
You must take your medicine on time.

355
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:27,760
I am not taking it.

356
00:18:28,280 --> 00:18:31,120
If you will not listen to me,
then at least listen to the doctor.

357
00:18:31,800 --> 00:18:34,599
Your emotions
and blood pressure are unstable.

358
00:18:34,600 --> 00:18:36,319
You need to take it on time.

359
00:18:36,320 --> 00:18:37,720
I am not taking it.

360
00:18:53,240 --> 00:18:54,360
Here.

361
00:19:15,120 --> 00:19:17,400
I will not be able
to take care of you in future.

362
00:19:22,160 --> 00:19:23,640
Take good care of yourself.

363
00:19:28,920 --> 00:19:30,240
Fengling.

364
00:20:00,320 --> 00:20:01,960
I am sorry.

365
00:20:06,320 --> 00:20:08,000
I did not take good care of you.

366
00:20:09,840 --> 00:20:11,240
I should not have

367
00:20:13,960 --> 00:20:16,480
sent you away.

368
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:17,489
That is enough.

369
00:20:17,489 --> 00:20:20,079
I should have gone
to bring you back, but I was too late.

370
00:20:20,080 --> 00:20:21,439
Stop.

371
00:20:21,440 --> 00:20:22,680
I

372
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:25,559
as a grown man,

373
00:20:25,560 --> 00:20:28,400
I have been holding this in for so long.

374
00:20:34,840 --> 00:20:36,160
Judge Shen,

375
00:20:37,640 --> 00:20:39,680
we are not getting divorced.

376
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:43,120
All right.

377
00:20:46,200 --> 00:20:48,560
Yuanbao is waiting for us at home.

378
00:20:49,160 --> 00:20:50,600
Let us go home.

379
00:21:15,120 --> 00:21:16,359
Ms. Qin,

380
00:21:16,360 --> 00:21:19,079
what did you think of today's meeting?

381
00:21:19,080 --> 00:21:21,360
I think it was very meaningful.

382
00:21:21,560 --> 00:21:22,359
Legal aid

383
00:21:22,360 --> 00:21:23,279
can help many people

384
00:21:23,280 --> 00:21:24,399
who truly need it.

385
00:21:24,400 --> 00:21:25,759
And I have thought about it,

386
00:21:25,760 --> 00:21:27,239
if I have time on weekends,

387
00:21:27,240 --> 00:21:29,000
I would like to come
to Chenxi Legal Aid Center

388
00:21:29,160 --> 00:21:30,840
and take part in legal aid work.

389
00:21:31,120 --> 00:21:32,159
That would be great.

390
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:34,000
Some lawyers who came before

391
00:21:34,040 --> 00:21:35,919
also spoke very positively at first,

392
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:37,679
but when they actually saw

393
00:21:37,680 --> 00:21:39,680
the people who needed help,

394
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:42,279
some of them backed out.

395
00:21:42,280 --> 00:21:43,560
Why?

396
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:46,159
Maybe

397
00:21:46,160 --> 00:21:49,240
they were not truly committed
to doing legal aid.

398
00:21:50,640 --> 00:21:51,959
Do not worry.

399
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:53,159
Since I said I would come,

400
00:21:53,160 --> 00:21:54,680
I will definitely come.

401
00:21:55,480 --> 00:21:56,159
That is great.

402
00:21:56,160 --> 00:21:58,240
Then let us grab a meal together.

403
00:21:59,040 --> 00:22:02,080
I actually have something to handle later.
How about next time?

404
00:22:03,360 --> 00:22:04,440
Sure.

405
00:22:04,560 --> 00:22:06,239
I will head off first.

406
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:07,480
See you.

407
00:22:14,080 --> 00:22:15,400
Thank you, Ms. Shu.

408
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:19,280
Your case has been mediated?

409
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:20,479
Yes.

410
00:22:20,480 --> 00:22:22,360
Both sides finally reached an agreement.

411
00:22:22,360 --> 00:22:24,199
The two younger ones
will stay with their grandmother,

412
00:22:24,200 --> 00:22:25,719
and the older one
will stay with the mother.

413
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:27,560
It is not a perfect outcome,

414
00:22:27,680 --> 00:22:28,999
but for now,

415
00:22:29,000 --> 00:22:31,720
it is the best arrangement
for the children.

416
00:22:32,360 --> 00:22:34,040
How about you?

417
00:22:34,640 --> 00:22:36,080
I have finished mine as well.

418
00:22:36,560 --> 00:22:38,439
In the end,
both parties chose to reconcile

419
00:22:38,440 --> 00:22:39,600
and decided not to divorce.

420
00:22:40,040 --> 00:22:41,199
So,

421
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:42,799
this morning, you and Xiang Hui

422
00:22:42,800 --> 00:22:45,119
were busy in the courtroom,

423
00:22:45,120 --> 00:22:45,959
was it this case?

424
00:22:45,960 --> 00:22:46,999
Yes.

425
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:48,680
I made a few small arrangements.

426
00:22:49,640 --> 00:22:51,080
There are

427
00:22:51,160 --> 00:22:53,719
indeed some issues between them,

428
00:22:53,720 --> 00:22:55,720
but the foundation
of their relationship is still strong.

429
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:57,719
She takes good care of him,

430
00:22:57,720 --> 00:23:00,159
and he has grown used to her care.

431
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:01,759
Although neither
of them says it out loud,

432
00:23:01,760 --> 00:23:02,719
deep down,

433
00:23:02,720 --> 00:23:04,519
they still care about each other.

434
00:23:04,520 --> 00:23:06,080
Neither of them can truly let go.

435
00:23:06,480 --> 00:23:07,599
So I thought,

436
00:23:07,600 --> 00:23:08,239
in court,

437
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:10,239
I would help you both realize this,

438
00:23:10,240 --> 00:23:12,000
which would also make mediation easier.

439
00:23:13,880 --> 00:23:15,159
It seems during this time,

440
00:23:15,160 --> 00:23:17,840
you have really grown
in the Family Court.

441
00:23:18,360 --> 00:23:21,640
You have even learned to take
an unconventional approach in mediating cases.

442
00:23:22,200 --> 00:23:23,719
A few months ago,

443
00:23:23,720 --> 00:23:25,319
you were still the Shen Xiezhi

444
00:23:25,320 --> 00:23:27,840
who could decide three cases
in one morning.

445
00:23:30,520 --> 00:23:32,760
I have indeed been through a lot lately,

446
00:23:33,280 --> 00:23:34,800
and I have grown a great deal.

447
00:23:36,520 --> 00:23:37,759
There is a saying,

448
00:23:37,760 --> 00:23:39,039
if a person does not feel

449
00:23:39,040 --> 00:23:41,120
that their past self
from a year ago is unfamiliar,

450
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:43,240
then it means
they have made no progress.

451
00:23:48,320 --> 00:23:49,560
Xiezhi,

452
00:23:50,840 --> 00:23:53,000
you really are quite talented.

453
00:23:54,730 --> 00:23:57,150
Have you truly decided
not to stay in the Family Court?

454
00:24:03,040 --> 00:24:04,240
Ms. Shu,

455
00:24:04,680 --> 00:24:06,120
you know that

456
00:24:06,840 --> 00:24:09,640
going to the High Court
has always been my goal.

457
00:24:12,600 --> 00:24:13,960
I understand.

458
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:16,520
It is just a pity

459
00:24:16,640 --> 00:24:20,200
the Family Court will lose someone
as capable as you.

460
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:33,639
You two,

461
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:35,519
is there anything else
you would like to eat?

462
00:24:35,520 --> 00:24:37,240
Do not be upset.

463
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:39,279
Just tell me what you want to eat.

464
00:24:39,280 --> 00:24:40,519
After buying it,

465
00:24:40,520 --> 00:24:43,320
we will go home
and have the nanny cook for you.

466
00:24:43,560 --> 00:24:44,439
Do not worry,

467
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:46,280
once we get home,

468
00:24:46,360 --> 00:24:50,119
I will take very good care of you.

469
00:24:50,120 --> 00:24:51,559
Much better

470
00:24:51,560 --> 00:24:53,319
than your mother ever did.

471
00:24:53,320 --> 00:24:55,160
That is enough, Mom.

472
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:56,759
Can you say less?

473
00:24:56,760 --> 00:24:58,760
If you are buying something,
then go quickly.

474
00:24:59,600 --> 00:25:00,840
All right.

475
00:25:01,840 --> 00:25:03,639
I will be back soon.

476
00:25:03,640 --> 00:25:04,839
Do not look at your phone.

477
00:25:04,840 --> 00:25:05,679
Keep an eye on them.

478
00:25:05,680 --> 00:25:06,719
What phone am I looking at?

479
00:25:06,720 --> 00:25:07,839
Fine, just go.

480
00:25:07,840 --> 00:25:09,439
Wait, baby.

481
00:25:09,440 --> 00:25:10,800
Slow down.

482
00:25:16,920 --> 00:25:20,360
(Candied Hawthorn)

483
00:25:21,840 --> 00:25:23,560
Candied hawthorn.

484
00:25:27,680 --> 00:25:30,039
Dad, I want candied hawthorn.

485
00:25:30,040 --> 00:25:31,079
What candied hawthorn?

486
00:25:31,080 --> 00:25:32,359
Where would you even find that?

487
00:25:32,360 --> 00:25:34,760
Dad, it is over there.

488
00:25:36,280 --> 00:25:38,600
I want candied hawthorn too.

489
00:25:38,800 --> 00:25:39,159
This...

490
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:40,319
We want it.

491
00:25:40,320 --> 00:25:43,159
What is so good about candied hawthorn?
We have plenty of good food at home.

492
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:44,119
After your grandma gets back,

493
00:25:44,120 --> 00:25:45,399
we will go home and eat, okay?

494
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:47,199
We want it.

495
00:25:47,200 --> 00:25:51,840
We want it.

496
00:25:51,960 --> 00:25:54,199
All right. I will go buy it for you.

497
00:25:54,200 --> 00:25:55,879
You two stay in the car

498
00:25:55,880 --> 00:25:57,000
and do not run around.

499
00:25:57,880 --> 00:26:00,760
So troublesome.
Why candied hawthorn of all things?

500
00:26:09,760 --> 00:26:11,200
Dad is leaving.

501
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:38,079
Slow down.

502
00:26:38,080 --> 00:26:39,519
You will fall again
if you are not careful.

503
00:26:39,520 --> 00:26:39,959
It is fine.

504
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:40,959
Why are you in such a hurry?

505
00:26:40,960 --> 00:26:41,759
How can I not be?

506
00:26:41,760 --> 00:26:42,559
What if later

507
00:26:42,560 --> 00:26:44,399
Yuanbao wakes up and cannot find us?

508
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:45,879
I will call him in a bit.

509
00:26:45,880 --> 00:26:46,319
Wait.

510
00:26:46,320 --> 00:26:48,440
I... I will call.

511
00:26:51,600 --> 00:26:53,319
So many missed calls.

512
00:26:53,320 --> 00:26:54,199
Who is it?

513
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:55,840
(Li)

514
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,480
Li.

515
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:00,629
Li.

516
00:27:00,630 --> 00:27:01,879
Mr. Wang,

517
00:27:01,880 --> 00:27:03,760
you finally saw the phone.

518
00:27:05,080 --> 00:27:06,279
What is going on?

519
00:27:06,280 --> 00:27:07,639
Yuanbao just ran out,

520
00:27:07,640 --> 00:27:09,559
said he was going to find you.
We could not stop him.

521
00:27:09,560 --> 00:27:11,000
Have you run into him?

522
00:27:12,360 --> 00:27:13,800
What did you say?

523
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:15,360
This...

524
00:27:41,560 --> 00:27:42,879
Do you want one?

525
00:27:42,880 --> 00:27:44,559
Where are your parents?

526
00:27:44,560 --> 00:27:46,480
Why is it just the two of you?

527
00:27:46,560 --> 00:27:48,520
Go find your parents to buy it.

528
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:52,719
Zero, one, one, one... one, one.

529
00:27:52,720 --> 00:27:54,440
Five yuan.

530
00:27:54,520 --> 00:27:55,640
Five yuan each.

531
00:28:09,120 --> 00:28:11,480
That is enough. Five yuan.

532
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:32,240
Dad.

533
00:28:32,480 --> 00:28:33,319
Mom.

534
00:28:33,320 --> 00:28:35,480
Mom is at the secret base.

535
00:28:36,160 --> 00:28:37,600
Ba... Base.

536
00:28:40,480 --> 00:28:41,720
Danger.

537
00:28:41,840 --> 00:28:43,280
No dad,

538
00:28:44,880 --> 00:28:46,400
no dad. It is dangerous.

539
00:28:51,920 --> 00:28:54,359
Add two.

540
00:28:54,360 --> 00:28:55,880
Do you want two more?

541
00:28:56,040 --> 00:28:56,800
Yes.

542
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:11,200
Shen Xiezhi.

543
00:29:26,200 --> 00:29:27,520
I

544
00:29:31,520 --> 00:29:32,559
waited here for you

545
00:29:32,560 --> 00:29:34,320
because I wanted to tell you something.

546
00:29:38,280 --> 00:29:40,480
You are about to go to the High Court,

547
00:29:41,320 --> 00:29:43,280
and become a judge there.

548
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:46,520
We will have

549
00:29:46,600 --> 00:29:48,000
fewer chances to meet in the future.

550
00:29:48,560 --> 00:29:51,760
I never had the chance
to congratulate you in person before.

551
00:29:52,880 --> 00:29:54,240
Congratulations.

552
00:29:55,600 --> 00:29:58,040
You have finally achieved your goal.

553
00:30:03,000 --> 00:30:04,040
Thank you.

554
00:30:04,840 --> 00:30:06,039
I think

555
00:30:06,040 --> 00:30:08,640
we will still have many chances
to meet again.

556
00:30:09,920 --> 00:30:12,640
After all, you are now
a lawyer at a top-tier law firm.

557
00:30:13,320 --> 00:30:15,160
Maybe one day,

558
00:30:15,600 --> 00:30:17,080
we will meet again in court.

559
00:30:20,640 --> 00:30:22,160
Ronghe has a strong reputation,

560
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:24,840
and the cases you handle
will be more complex.

561
00:30:25,560 --> 00:30:28,280
Naturally, you will face
more challenges and scrutiny.

562
00:30:30,040 --> 00:30:31,840
You need to learn to protect yourself.

563
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:35,400
I believe you can do it.

564
00:30:38,720 --> 00:30:40,159
Thank you.

565
00:30:40,160 --> 00:30:41,480
But,

566
00:30:41,840 --> 00:30:43,159
I think in the future,

567
00:30:43,160 --> 00:30:44,800
we will not meet in court.

568
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:47,600
(Client Mr. Wang)

569
00:30:49,840 --> 00:30:51,160
What do you mean?

570
00:30:51,760 --> 00:30:53,360
You are leaving Ronghe Law Firm?

571
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:56,519
But I saw the firm's announcement.

572
00:30:56,520 --> 00:30:58,600
Was the misunderstanding
not already cleared up?

573
00:30:58,760 --> 00:31:01,120
No, I am still working
at Ronghe Law Firm.

574
00:31:01,240 --> 00:31:03,239
It is just that the firm
has reassigned my work

575
00:31:03,240 --> 00:31:04,799
to non-litigation matters.

576
00:31:04,800 --> 00:31:06,160
Non-litigation?

577
00:31:07,360 --> 00:31:09,200
Why switch to non-litigation
all of a sudden?

578
00:31:11,480 --> 00:31:14,000
Actually, what I mean is,

579
00:31:14,960 --> 00:31:16,720
I will not be appearing
in court anymore.

580
00:31:20,600 --> 00:31:22,240
That means between you and me,

581
00:31:22,320 --> 00:31:24,040
there will be no conflict.

582
00:31:33,760 --> 00:31:35,000
Then

583
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:39,400
would you still
be willing to be with me?

584
00:31:47,960 --> 00:31:49,760
(Client Mr. Wang)

585
00:31:51,320 --> 00:31:52,800
You should take the call first.

586
00:31:56,860 --> 00:31:58,030
Hello, Mr. Wang.

587
00:31:59,160 --> 00:32:00,400
What?

588
00:32:02,560 --> 00:32:05,040
All right, I understand.
I will be there right away.

589
00:32:08,600 --> 00:32:10,039
My client just now,

590
00:32:10,040 --> 00:32:12,200
his son suddenly went missing.

591
00:32:13,120 --> 00:32:14,240
Then

592
00:32:15,560 --> 00:32:17,280
you should go help look for him.

593
00:32:19,800 --> 00:32:21,079
Wait for me.

594
00:32:21,080 --> 00:32:22,400
Wait for me to come back.

595
00:32:33,040 --> 00:32:34,199
Hello,

596
00:32:34,200 --> 00:32:35,519
this is Shu Jing from the Family Court

597
00:32:35,520 --> 00:32:37,040
of Qingcheng Court.

598
00:32:37,080 --> 00:32:38,439
Chief Judge Shu,

599
00:32:38,440 --> 00:32:40,479
my two children are missing.

600
00:32:40,480 --> 00:32:42,879
What? Both children are missing?

601
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:44,120
Yes.

602
00:32:44,200 --> 00:32:46,119
Let me tell you, Chief Judge Shu,

603
00:32:46,120 --> 00:32:48,920
it must have
been Shi Xiaomei who took them.

604
00:32:49,520 --> 00:32:50,879
Ever since we left the court,

605
00:32:50,880 --> 00:32:52,519
she must have

606
00:32:52,520 --> 00:32:55,280
been quietly following us.

607
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:56,919
Please do not jump to conclusions yet.

608
00:32:56,920 --> 00:32:57,879
Call the police immediately.

609
00:32:57,880 --> 00:32:59,480
I will call Shi Xiaomei.

610
00:33:01,680 --> 00:33:03,160
Mom, what did she say?

611
00:33:04,040 --> 00:33:06,439
What did she say? Look at you.

612
00:33:06,440 --> 00:33:07,760
Call the police.

613
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:10,440
Du, hurry.

614
00:33:11,600 --> 00:33:12,599
What about Du then?

615
00:33:12,600 --> 00:33:14,000
- Ms. Shu.
- Should Du come with us?

616
00:33:14,800 --> 00:33:16,520
What is going on?
Why are you in such a hurry?

617
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:18,479
The child's
younger siblings are missing.

618
00:33:18,480 --> 00:33:20,119
We are about to go look for them.

619
00:33:20,120 --> 00:33:21,239
This is the child's mother.

620
00:33:21,240 --> 00:33:22,119
This is Lawyer Qin.

621
00:33:22,120 --> 00:33:23,199
Hello.

622
00:33:23,200 --> 00:33:23,999
Do you need help?

623
00:33:24,000 --> 00:33:24,959
I can go with you.

624
00:33:24,960 --> 00:33:26,359
No, it is fine. We can handle it.

625
00:33:26,360 --> 00:33:27,800
You should go take care
of your own matters.

626
00:33:29,920 --> 00:33:31,120
The child is still young.

627
00:33:31,120 --> 00:33:32,959
It would be inconvenient
for you to bring her along.

628
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:33,680
How about this?

629
00:33:34,120 --> 00:33:36,200
I'm waiting for someone here.
I can help to take care the child for you.

630
00:33:36,200 --> 00:33:36,919
That...

631
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:38,279
That would be too much trouble for you.

632
00:33:38,280 --> 00:33:39,679
That... That works too.

633
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:41,559
Du, stay with this sister.

634
00:33:41,560 --> 00:33:43,960
I will come back to get you
after finding your siblings.

635
00:33:44,360 --> 00:33:46,119
Listen to her and do not run around.

636
00:33:46,120 --> 00:33:47,359
- Thank you, Ms. Qin.
- It is nothing.

637
00:33:47,360 --> 00:33:48,019
We'll be back soon.

638
00:33:48,019 --> 00:33:49,360
When Xiezhi returns,
I will ask him to come find you.

639
00:33:49,360 --> 00:33:50,520
Go on, hurry.

640
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:54,840
Your name is Du, right?

641
00:33:55,520 --> 00:33:57,760
Let me help you carry your bag. Come.

642
00:33:58,360 --> 00:34:00,000
All right, sit here for a while.

643
00:34:00,720 --> 00:34:01,599
Yuanbao,

644
00:34:01,600 --> 00:34:04,040
can you take us to the secret base?

645
00:34:07,160 --> 00:34:07,919
Base.

646
00:34:07,920 --> 00:34:10,440
We do not have money for the bus.

647
00:34:15,960 --> 00:34:17,400
No dad. Dangerous.

648
00:34:18,880 --> 00:34:20,240
Dangerous.

649
00:34:22,920 --> 00:34:23,719
Together.

650
00:34:23,720 --> 00:34:26,280
Great. Thank you, Yuanbao.

651
00:34:30,080 --> 00:34:31,200
Together.

652
00:34:32,880 --> 00:34:35,400
Where do you think he could have gone?

653
00:34:38,000 --> 00:34:39,199
This... This...

654
00:34:39,200 --> 00:34:40,720
This child...

655
00:34:43,040 --> 00:34:43,959
Sir, madam,

656
00:34:43,960 --> 00:34:45,239
has Yuanbao been found?

657
00:34:45,240 --> 00:34:45,959
No.

658
00:34:45,960 --> 00:34:50,039
The neighbors helped search all around,
and we have been waiting here the whole time,

659
00:34:50,040 --> 00:34:51,199
in case he suddenly comes back.

660
00:34:51,200 --> 00:34:53,000
If he is really lost,

661
00:34:53,040 --> 00:34:53,999
what are we supposed to do?

662
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:54,919
Exactly.

663
00:34:54,920 --> 00:34:56,679
Sir, madam, please do not panic yet.

664
00:34:56,680 --> 00:34:57,999
Yuanbao is a grown man.

665
00:34:58,000 --> 00:35:00,240
He will be all right.
Let us think of a way together.

666
00:35:00,680 --> 00:35:01,639
If all the nearby places

667
00:35:01,640 --> 00:35:03,559
have already been searched,

668
00:35:03,560 --> 00:35:04,399
does Yuanbao have anywhere

669
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:06,960
he especially likes to go,
somewhere farther away?

670
00:35:07,240 --> 00:35:07,839
No.

671
00:35:07,840 --> 00:35:10,279
If it were farther away,
he would have taken the bus.

672
00:35:10,280 --> 00:35:11,639
Taken the bus?

673
00:35:11,640 --> 00:35:12,599
If he took the bus,

674
00:35:12,600 --> 00:35:14,679
we should be able to trace it
through his ID information.

675
00:35:14,680 --> 00:35:15,199
How about this?

676
00:35:15,200 --> 00:35:16,639
Send me Yuanbao's ID card,

677
00:35:16,640 --> 00:35:17,959
and I will ask someone to check.

678
00:35:17,960 --> 00:35:19,120
All right.

679
00:35:22,160 --> 00:35:24,079
Please be careful.

680
00:35:24,080 --> 00:35:25,560
Where are you?

681
00:35:25,760 --> 00:35:28,079
Hello, you little kid, where are you?

682
00:35:28,080 --> 00:35:29,320
We are here.

683
00:35:29,640 --> 00:35:30,999
(Tianhai Bus)
Hurry up.

684
00:35:31,000 --> 00:35:33,160
Yuanbao, we are here.

685
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:34,279
Yuanbao, come on.

686
00:35:34,280 --> 00:35:35,680
Come on.

687
00:35:35,880 --> 00:35:39,160
We are here. Come on.

688
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:43,559
- Yuanbao, look.
- The secret base is over there.

689
00:35:43,560 --> 00:35:45,240
The secret base is right there.

690
00:35:46,760 --> 00:35:47,960
There.

691
00:35:52,920 --> 00:35:54,279
Okay.

692
00:35:54,280 --> 00:35:55,639
All right. Thanks.

693
00:35:55,640 --> 00:35:57,560
I am hanging up. I will treat you
to a meal another time.

694
00:35:57,840 --> 00:35:58,759
Sir, madam,

695
00:35:58,760 --> 00:35:59,519
we found it.

696
00:35:59,520 --> 00:36:01,319
Yuanbao really did take the bus.

697
00:36:01,320 --> 00:36:02,319
He took Route 13

698
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:03,839
and got off at Jinghongyuan Station.

699
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:05,359
Come on, let us go find him.

700
00:36:05,360 --> 00:36:07,880
- Okay.
- Hurry.

701
00:36:08,440 --> 00:36:09,600
Let us go.

702
00:36:18,240 --> 00:36:19,479
Do not worry.

703
00:36:19,480 --> 00:36:20,039
They

704
00:36:20,040 --> 00:36:22,440
will definitely help you
find your younger brother and sister.

705
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:24,560
They have all gone to look for them.

706
00:36:25,440 --> 00:36:26,760
I know.

707
00:36:31,800 --> 00:36:33,440
You know all that.

708
00:36:33,520 --> 00:36:35,159
Help me think, okay?

709
00:36:35,160 --> 00:36:37,520
If they got lost, where would they go?

710
00:36:40,160 --> 00:36:41,840
Think carefully.

711
00:36:42,440 --> 00:36:44,920
If the adults cannot find them,

712
00:36:45,120 --> 00:36:46,880
and they run into bad people,

713
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:48,319
they will be in danger.

714
00:36:48,320 --> 00:36:50,280
Bad people might take them away.

715
00:36:52,680 --> 00:36:54,720
They

716
00:36:55,600 --> 00:36:57,839
would really be taken by bad people?

717
00:36:57,840 --> 00:36:59,200
Of course.

718
00:36:59,400 --> 00:37:00,919
Think about it, these two children

719
00:37:00,920 --> 00:37:02,279
do not have a phone

720
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:03,920
and have no adult with them.

721
00:37:04,240 --> 00:37:05,879
If they cry for help,

722
00:37:05,880 --> 00:37:07,360
no one will respond.

723
00:37:08,080 --> 00:37:10,000
If something dangerous happens,

724
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:12,599
you might never

725
00:37:12,600 --> 00:37:14,560
see your brother and sister again.

726
00:37:24,240 --> 00:37:25,799
Think carefully,

727
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:27,480
where might they be?

728
00:37:31,400 --> 00:37:33,400
We said before,

729
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:36,560
if we got separated,

730
00:37:36,880 --> 00:37:38,439
we would find a way

731
00:37:38,440 --> 00:37:40,359
to meet at the secret base.

732
00:37:40,360 --> 00:37:41,920
Secret base?

733
00:37:42,880 --> 00:37:44,280
Where is it?

734
00:37:44,760 --> 00:37:47,360
Is it a place you often go to play?

735
00:37:50,400 --> 00:37:51,640
Then how about this,

736
00:37:52,320 --> 00:37:54,000
I will go with you.

737
00:37:54,960 --> 00:37:56,199
Would you be willing

738
00:37:56,200 --> 00:37:58,200
to take me to your secret base?

739
00:38:09,720 --> 00:38:11,480
Hurry up, Yuanbao.

740
00:38:12,120 --> 00:38:13,280
Quick.

741
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:20,880
Look, that is our secret base.

742
00:38:23,160 --> 00:38:25,400
This is our secret base.

743
00:38:25,520 --> 00:38:26,720
Base.

744
00:38:26,920 --> 00:38:29,280
My sister and I found it.

745
00:38:29,480 --> 00:38:30,639
No one else knows.

746
00:38:30,640 --> 00:38:32,560
Do not tell anyone.

747
00:38:43,440 --> 00:38:44,279
Sir, madam,

748
00:38:44,280 --> 00:38:45,839
we have searched around the station.

749
00:38:45,840 --> 00:38:46,999
This is a park.

750
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:48,719
I think Yuanbao might be inside.

751
00:38:48,720 --> 00:38:50,080
Let us go in and take a look.

752
00:38:50,480 --> 00:38:51,879
Okay, let us go.

753
00:38:51,880 --> 00:38:52,920
Let us go.

754
00:39:08,920 --> 00:39:10,039
(Jinghongyuan Park)
(Ms. Shu.)

755
00:39:10,040 --> 00:39:11,079
(Du brought me here)

756
00:39:11,080 --> 00:39:11,959
(to look for Meng and Bei.)

757
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:12,679
There is news about the children.

758
00:39:12,680 --> 00:39:13,700
(I will send you the location.)

759
00:39:13,700 --> 00:39:14,960
Found them?

760
00:39:15,480 --> 00:39:17,120
At Jinghongyuan Park.

761
00:39:17,200 --> 00:39:19,280
Jinghongyuan Park.

762
00:39:21,800 --> 00:39:23,559
Madam, there is news about the children.

763
00:39:23,560 --> 00:39:25,320
They are at Jinghongyuan Park.

764
00:39:26,480 --> 00:39:32,200
One, two, three, four, five, six,

765
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:36,800
seven, eight, nine, zero.

766
00:39:36,960 --> 00:39:38,600
Hide well.

767
00:39:38,960 --> 00:39:40,160
Hide well.

768
00:40:03,600 --> 00:40:04,880
Six, six.

769
00:40:05,800 --> 00:40:08,879
(The breakdown of a family
caused by adult conflict)

770
00:40:08,880 --> 00:40:12,320
(can make children feel abandoned.)

771
00:40:12,440 --> 00:40:15,200
(They may
hide their hearts in the dark.)

772
00:40:15,880 --> 00:40:17,639
(Our responsibility)

773
00:40:17,640 --> 00:40:20,399
(is to help them
step out of the shadows,)

774
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:22,360
(and return to the light.)

775
00:40:37,400 --> 00:40:39,760
This is your secret base?

776
00:40:40,160 --> 00:40:42,400
Yes, almost there. It is just ahead.

777
00:40:45,400 --> 00:40:46,760
How much farther?

778
00:40:47,400 --> 00:40:48,880
We are almost there.

779
00:40:51,040 --> 00:40:52,920
This is our secret base.

780
00:40:55,160 --> 00:40:57,440
These are my brother
and sister's schoolbags.

781
00:40:58,760 --> 00:40:59,839
Meng.

782
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:01,320
Meng, Bei.

783
00:41:02,600 --> 00:41:03,799
Meng, Bei.

784
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:04,679
Du.

785
00:41:04,680 --> 00:41:06,040
Du.

786
00:41:09,550 --> 00:41:10,259
You two little ones

787
00:41:10,260 --> 00:41:11,919
really hid here.

788
00:41:11,920 --> 00:41:12,719
You finally came.

789
00:41:12,720 --> 00:41:14,239
Come with me.

790
00:41:14,240 --> 00:41:15,240
Let us go.

791
00:41:18,640 --> 00:41:19,960
Who are you?

792
00:41:20,400 --> 00:41:22,480
He is our friend.

793
00:41:23,400 --> 00:41:25,320
He brought us here.

794
00:41:29,200 --> 00:41:30,319
All right.

795
00:41:30,320 --> 00:41:31,479
Come with me first.

796
00:41:31,480 --> 00:41:32,799
Your family is worried sick.

797
00:41:32,800 --> 00:41:35,560
I do not want to go with Grandma.

798
00:41:37,920 --> 00:41:39,079
Why not?

799
00:41:39,080 --> 00:41:41,600
I want to stay with Mom.

800
00:41:43,160 --> 00:41:44,359
Okay, we will go find Mom.

801
00:41:44,360 --> 00:41:46,160
We will go find Mom, okay?

802
00:41:47,280 --> 00:41:48,439
Hurry, talk to him.

803
00:41:48,440 --> 00:41:50,359
Bei, let us go find Mom.

804
00:41:50,360 --> 00:41:52,279
Mom will be worried if you stay here.

805
00:41:52,280 --> 00:41:53,079
It is dangerous here.

806
00:41:53,080 --> 00:41:54,079
What if there are bad people?

807
00:41:54,080 --> 00:41:55,519
Mom is very worried.

808
00:41:55,520 --> 00:41:56,239
Okay?

809
00:41:56,240 --> 00:41:57,679
Yes, your family is very worried.

810
00:41:57,680 --> 00:41:58,519
Let us go, let us go.

811
00:41:58,520 --> 00:41:59,360
Come on.

812
00:41:59,700 --> 00:42:00,639
- Take your bag.
- Go, hurry.

813
00:42:00,640 --> 00:42:01,839
Yuanbao, we are going.

814
00:42:01,840 --> 00:42:03,640
Yuanbao, we are going.

815
00:42:05,120 --> 00:42:06,519
The bag is over there. I will get it.

816
00:42:06,520 --> 00:42:07,599
Let us go.

817
00:42:07,600 --> 00:42:08,760
Let us go.

818
00:42:10,560 --> 00:42:12,519
Do not run around again, understand?

819
00:42:12,520 --> 00:42:14,240
There they are.

820
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:15,359
Bei.

821
00:42:15,360 --> 00:42:16,039
Meng.

822
00:42:16,040 --> 00:42:17,119
Where did you two run off to?

823
00:42:17,120 --> 00:42:19,239
You scared me to death.

824
00:42:19,240 --> 00:42:19,999
I thought

825
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:21,559
you had been taken away.

826
00:42:21,560 --> 00:42:23,200
Where did you go?

827
00:42:24,480 --> 00:42:25,800
Who are you two?

828
00:42:28,160 --> 00:42:29,560
Meng, Bei.

829
00:42:31,080 --> 00:42:32,079
Meng, Bei.

830
00:42:32,080 --> 00:42:32,389
Bei.

831
00:42:32,390 --> 00:42:33,479
Mom.

832
00:42:33,480 --> 00:42:36,039
Why are you here?

833
00:42:36,040 --> 00:42:37,199
Did you not say before

834
00:42:37,200 --> 00:42:38,879
that the Mom took the children away?

835
00:42:38,880 --> 00:42:40,239
Now that Mom has come to see them,

836
00:42:40,240 --> 00:42:40,919
is that not normal?

837
00:42:40,920 --> 00:42:42,639
Enough. The decision has already
been made today.

838
00:42:42,640 --> 00:42:45,000
Ziping, take them back now.

839
00:42:45,080 --> 00:42:47,320
These two are not behaving. Come on.

840
00:42:47,440 --> 00:42:47,999
Come on.

841
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:48,479
Hurry up, go.

842
00:42:48,480 --> 00:42:49,279
Go.

843
00:42:49,280 --> 00:42:50,799
